  <notepads>
    <notepad>
      <note>This transformation retrieves data from a database and formulates a JSON request based on the system request, 
submits request to GPT and receives and parses the JSON result to create report summary. Be sensitive to your soft and hard API limits.

Parameters include:
SYSTEM - Objectives/purpose of the system, how the files are used to generate content
TOKEN - Your bearer token parameter as assigned by OpenAI.
TRIM - Whether to estimate tokens and trim the file before summarizing
MAXCHARS - How many chars to cut files at to before sending to model
MODEL - Which model to use, for example gpt-3.5-turbo
SUMMARY - Should the summary Assistant be run?</note>
